text: Asmi Shrestha () (born June 30, 1993 in Chitwan, Nepal is a Nepalese model, many beauty pageant titleholder and celebrity of the Nation. She has won the title of Miss Nepal in 2016 and participants of Miss World 2016. She had also won the title of Best Evening Gown, Miss Photogenic & Miss Personality sub titles. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models Category:Miss Nepal winners
